file.name: openapi.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Order Response
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /order-response:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/OrderResponse'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
components:
  schemas:
    OrderResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        orderId:
          type: string
        documents:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            properties:
              name:
                type: string
                example: doc1
              doc:
                type: string
                format: byte
                example: dXNlckBkb21haW4uY29tOnBhc3N3b3Jk
